e distributed in various sections of the Bible. Another aid for students is that all Hebrew references, other than in the ms., are given in a fully vocalized form.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 10. Jan 2022) 4aBible. 4aReligion. 4aStudy/Old Testament. 7aRELIGION / Biblical Studies / Old Testament.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertGorgias Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311074330240uhttps://doi.org/10.31826/978146324388340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781463243883423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781463243883/original  a978-3-11-074330-2  Gorgias Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK